creator: Nationwide Technologies Inc
descriptionHtml:
Our system is designed such that motor carrier and drivers can comply with HOS regulations by tracking driver's duty status, location and engine data.

Engine and location data is captured by a device mounted in the vehicle which then forwards the data to the app to later be used in combination with the driver's reported duty status. The app also serves as a method for Drivers to check and transfer eRODS data to the FMCSA in case of a roadside inspection
descriptionShort: An app used for HOS compliance and part the Keep Trackin ELD ecosystem.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
1. Now the app screen is locked to portrait irrespective of device sensors and auto rotate feature,
2.  Remember me under login page not working issue were fixed,
3. App logo and version is displayed in 'about' section under menu,
4. When Driver enters VIN number, the letters are converted to upper case before manipulating it.
5. PC going to DRIVE automatically issue were fixed,
6. Dashboard header name changing were fixed,
7. 'VIN no not available' text is highlighted in red color.
